Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.62,0:01:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,新年了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.56,0:01:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.36,0:01:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好安静啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.19,0:01:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.05,0:01:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.79,0:01:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢抽烟的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.73,0:01:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你不用介意我的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.67,0:01:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.53,0:01:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,仔细想想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.94,0:01:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,现在也不是吸烟的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.35,0:02:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸我来吧\N不用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.95,0:02:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这点小事我自己来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.26,0:02:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,美丽新娘的禁忌温泉\N给公公搓背然后……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.50,0:03:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.70,0:03:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我也没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.03,0:03:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为能在休假前 完成工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.97,0:03:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,但是只有我和爸爸一起……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.31,0:03:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那你直接说取消不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.25,0:03:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道今天是什么日子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.99,0:03:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.46,0:03:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我很努力的为了能休假工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,就一晚而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.06,0:03:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.27,0:04:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起啦\N总之你们先过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.21,0:04:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,之后我过来\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.74,0:04:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,之后我过来\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.02,0:04:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,结果那个家伙还是不来啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.09,0:04:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.76,0:04:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他说之后会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.50,0:04:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我们回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.84,0:04:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这么难得来旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.11,0:04:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.98,0:04:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.75,0:05:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,既然这么难得来到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.02,0:05:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,由衣\N要不你去洗个澡？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.83,0:05:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不用了\N要不爸爸你先去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.97,0:05:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,明明是结婚纪念日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.31,0:05:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,良一真是过分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.78,0:05:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我真是打扰你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.52,0:05:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,由衣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.65,0:05:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这个旅店是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.72,0:06:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我和良一的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.46,0:06:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,蜜月旅行住的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.33,0:06:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那是30年前的事了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.94,0:06:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我先去散步
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.48,0:06:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,由衣去洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.35,0:06:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一起去逛吧\N可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.37,0:06:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.57,0:06:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,就当做代替妈妈\N重温你们的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.11,0:08:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好久没有来这里了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.72,0:08:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,回忆起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.12,0:08:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈好像还给我搓背啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.33,0:08:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.53,0:08:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我今天给你搓背吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.80,0:08:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我好像说了奇怪的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.54,0:08:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不要吓我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.55,0:08:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那么我先去洗澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.29,0:08:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,一会你可以慢慢地洗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.95,0:09:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,还是我帮你洗吧？\N啊，嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.79,0:10:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,如果良一和爸爸那样温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.33,0:10:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他会珍惜你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.41,0:10:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不过在这个时候工作\N真是不应该
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.95,0:10:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他是我养大的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.22,0:11:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前也常被妈妈说\N总是忙着工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,想起来真是对不起她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.11,0:11:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.11,0:11:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我给你搓背吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.69,0:12:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.52,0:12:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,想要像爸爸那么温柔的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.19,0:12:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要像妈妈那样温柔的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.93,0:12:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我还不够温柔是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.21,0:25:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.88,0:25:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.11,0:25:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,良一
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.12,0:25:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,还没有联系你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.72,0:26:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.07,0:26:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,正赶上吃饭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.74,0:26:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,良一
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.48,0:26:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.34,0:26:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,迟点再说教啦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.15,0:26:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我可是工作\N你们玩得爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.88,0:26:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,还要骂我真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.11,0:27:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,搞快点
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.82,0:27:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我说你快点！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.58,0:29:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,舔更多
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.88,0:30:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.88,0:30:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,用胸部夹着
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.25,0:31:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,用乳头摩擦
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.83,0:32:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,啊～摩擦更快点
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.05,0:32:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,用嘴巴舔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.66,0:32:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你的给我舔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.53,0:33:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.00,0:33:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.11,0:37:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.50,0:39:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,啊~ 高潮！高潮！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.31,0:39:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,啊~ 高潮！高潮！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.73,0:39:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.03,0:41:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,啊~ 要射
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.80,0:41:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.71,0:42:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,明天我要先回去工作了\N你们在这里玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.06,0:42:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但是怎么可以
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.99,0:42:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我也没办法啊\N工作嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.80,0:42:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,过来我这里\N但是
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.80,0:43:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,过来我这里\N但是
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.27,0:43:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.28,0:43:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,怕什么啊\N你寂寞不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.42,0:43:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,但是爸爸在隔壁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.20,0:43:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,过来我这里
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.58,0:44:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但是爸爸在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.91,0:44:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.05,0:44:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不怕啦
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.92,0:44:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不用介意
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.25,0:49:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好湿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.19,0:49:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.44,0:50:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.98,0:51:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.60,0:52:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,舔很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.14,0:54:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸会听到的
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.68,0:54:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.06,0:55:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,想要更多吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.98,0:56:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这里舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.93,0:56:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.14,0:56:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,舔我
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.28,0:57:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.51,0:58:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.23,1:00:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我要进去
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.56,1:00:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,后面来
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.96,1:05:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你上来
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.54,1:06:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,超舒服啊！
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.27,1:07:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮～高潮～啊啊啊！
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.35,1:10:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.96,1:11:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.47,1:11:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,啊~ 射了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.11,1:25:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以和你一起洗吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.52,1:26:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,良一呢
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.85,1:26:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,今天很早就走了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.13,1:26:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,说是要回去上班
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.80,1:26:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我打电话给他叫他回来\N等等，他走了也好
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.28,1:26:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我给你搓背吧
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.19,1:27:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不要这样
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.73,1:27:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经讨厌我了吗？\N我只想抱抱爸爸你
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.67,1:27:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那抱吧
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.23,1:35:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.70,1:35:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.71,1:35:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那更多吧
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.90,1:43:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,啊～舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:45:33.49,1:45:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,1:47:04.65,1:47:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,啊~ 高潮啊
Dialogue: 0,1:49:40.40,1:49:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,啊~ 舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,1:50:07.10,1:50:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:50:17.51,1:50:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,啊～射了
